media:group.media:title: 【ELITE EXORCIST MIKO】Tutorial Demonstration
media:group.media:description:
I revealed it on Twitter but Miko fangame now has a name! This video showcases the tutorial that'll teach gameplay basics, ending with a battle against Ame. You can't lose in the tutorial, so it's a chance to test things out and you'll be able to replay it at any time.

Sakura Miko: @Miko Ch. さくらみこ 
Watson Amelia: @Watson Amelia Ch. hololive-EN 

Music arrangements of:

Ochame Kinou - LamazeP
